  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK241">
<l>aruṭcelvañ celvattuṭ celvam poruṭcelvam</l>
<l>pūriyār kaṇṇu muḷa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of kindness is wealth of wealth, in as much as the wealth of property is possessed by the basest of men.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
